      "Against": "Lack of classic rash, although not always present.",
      "Support": "Well-supported"
    },
    "Fulminant gram-negative enteric sepsis": {
      "Supports": "History of varices/cirrhosis (translocation risk), diarrhea, rapid shock, multi-organ dysfunction.",
      "Against": "No obvious source of primary bacteremia initially identified on imaging (though bowel wall thickening present).",
      "Support": "Well-supported"
    },
